- You think I'm some kind of idiot?

266
00:22:09,666 --> 00:22:12,041
The South is nothing
but cliffs and ravines.

267
00:22:12,041 --> 00:22:14,541
- Yeah, that's true but
that's where I came from.

268
00:22:14,541 --> 00:22:16,541
- I don't care if you
were born from the rocks.

269
00:22:16,541 --> 00:22:17,750
You can't bring weapons in here.

270
00:22:17,750 --> 00:22:18,791
I'm taking it.

271
00:22:19,750 --> 00:22:21,500
(gasping)

272
00:22:21,500 --> 00:22:26,416
(struggling)

273
00:22:40,083 --> 00:22:41,541
Please, sir, there's a weapons ban

274
00:22:41,541 --> 00:22:43,041
being enforced on the city.

275
00:22:43,041 --> 00:22:45,416
Nobody's allowed weapons
within the city walls.

276
00:22:45,416 --> 00:22:47,750
Knives and swords could hurt good people.

277
00:22:47,750 --> 00:22:49,458
We don't want people to get hurt.

278
00:22:49,458 --> 00:22:52,083
- Blades ruin lives but so does revenge.

279
00:22:52,083 --> 00:22:53,208
- We're just following orders

280
00:22:53,208 --> 00:22:55,833
and keeping your sword temporarily, sir.

281
00:22:55,833 --> 00:22:57,833
Oh man, that long haired guy's good.

282
00:22:57,833 --> 00:22:59,166
I wonder where he's from.

283
00:22:59,166 --> 00:23:01,500
And you, you idiot, you
almost chopped my arm off.

284
00:23:01,500 --> 00:23:03,291
- [Quail] Sorry, Captain,
that was an accident.

285
00:23:08,791 --> 00:23:12,166
(foreboding music)

286
00:23:12,166 --> 00:23:14,083
- [Voiceover] What's Wind doing here?

287
00:23:14,083 --> 00:23:15,125
He's so drunk.

288
00:23:16,041 --> 00:23:16,666
- [Voiceover] I don't care.

289
00:23:16,666 --> 00:23:19,750
Anyone from Conquerer's
Clan needs to be dealt with.

290
00:23:19,750 --> 00:23:20,625
- [Voiceover] The master's coming.

291
00:23:23,958 --> 00:23:28,708
(mysterious music)

292
00:23:39,916 --> 00:23:40,750
- [Men] Mistress.

293
00:23:44,791 --> 00:23:47,000
- Miss Dream, he's the
renowned Whispering Wind

294
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:48,291
from the Conquerer's Clan.

295
00:23:48,291 --> 00:23:51,000
Should he awaken, we will
not be his equal in battle.

296
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:52,791
We should kill him before he wakes up.

297
00:23:54,291 --> 00:23:58,083
(monkey chattering)

298
00:23:58,083 --> 00:24:00,375
- I want to know exactly why he's here.

299
00:24:00,375 --> 00:24:01,708
Quickly, bring him inside.

300
00:24:03,833 --> 00:24:05,000
- We're only hiding here because

301
00:24:05,000 --> 00:24:07,041
we're trying to escape
from the Conquerer's Clan.

302
00:24:07,041 --> 00:24:08,750
His presence might expose us.

303
00:24:10,875 --> 00:24:11,833
- No, you're wrong.

304
00:24:11,833 --> 00:24:13,458
We're only hiding her because we want

305
00:24:13,458 --> 00:24:15,958
to get away from senseless violence.

306
00:24:15,958 --> 00:24:17,791
Just tell everyone to stay alert.

307
00:24:23,958 --> 00:24:25,916
(thunder booming)

308
00:24:30,500 --> 00:24:32,125
- Friends of the martial arts world,

309
00:24:32,125 --> 00:24:34,083
members of the Conquerer's Clan,

310
00:24:34,083 --> 00:24:37,416
in defending the clan, our
Lord Conquerer perished,

311
00:24:37,416 --> 00:24:40,000
killed by his own
disciples, Whispering Wind

312
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:42,750
and Striding Cloud, the
whole of Conquerer's Clan

313
00:24:42,750 --> 00:24:44,583
is sad and mournful now.

314
00:24:45,791 --> 00:24:48,875
Our kingdom needs his
king and ours is gone.

315
00:24:48,875 --> 00:24:50,875
Today, we shall announce that Tun Wong

316
00:24:50,875 --> 00:24:53,083
will ascend to the
position of clan leader.

317
00:24:54,125 --> 00:24:56,375
- Huh, Tun Wong as clan leader?

318
00:24:58,000 --> 00:24:59,166
(laughing)

319
00:25:00,625 --> 00:25:01,541
- [Duen Long] You're all right.

320
00:25:02,791 --> 00:25:05,666
So, why don't you let
me be your new leader?

321
00:25:05,666 --> 00:25:08,208
(whispering)

322
00:25:09,166 --> 00:25:10,458
- What are you doing here?

323
00:25:10,458 --> 00:25:12,625
You were thrown out of
the Conquerer's Clan.

324
00:25:12,625 --> 00:25:13,208
- How rude.

325
00:25:13,208 --> 00:25:14,333
I'm your new leader.

326
00:25:14,333 --> 00:25:16,125
How dare you speak to me like that.

327
00:25:16,125 --> 00:25:17,750
I'll make an example of you.

328
00:25:17,750 --> 00:25:19,541
- You don't have the skills, boy.

329
00:25:33,333 --> 00:25:34,500
(yelling)

330
00:25:41,791 --> 00:25:42,666
- Oh, you deserve that.

331
00:25:42,666 --> 00:25:44,083
You should've just let him be.

332
00:25:45,291 --> 00:25:49,500
(clanking)

333
00:25:55,166 --> 00:25:57,833
- This is why you have no
idea how to treat a lady.

334
00:25:58,875 --> 00:26:01,083
We don't often get such
a beautiful girl around.

335
00:26:09,333 --> 00:26:11,333
(whinnying)

336
00:26:11,333 --> 00:26:15,583
(wind howling)

337
00:26:19,708 --> 00:26:24,000
(birds cawing)

338
00:26:29,166 --> 00:26:34,166
(mysterious music)

339
00:26:48,333 --> 00:26:52,125
- Hmm, Conquerer, you
always did look down on me.

340
00:26:52,125 --> 00:26:54,791
But, you still met your end at
the hands of your disciples.

341
00:26:55,833 --> 00:26:58,833
Well now, have a good look at
who's succeeded your place.

342
00:26:59,791 --> 00:27:01,208
It's me, Duen Long.

343
00:27:04,666 --> 00:27:07,083
(bird cawing)

344
00:27:07,083 --> 00:27:11,166
(wind blowing)

345
00:27:12,166 --> 00:27:16,958
(suspenseful music)

346
00:27:52,750 --> 00:27:57,625
(birds chirping)

347
00:28:03,625 --> 00:28:05,250
(clinking)

348
00:28:07,875 --> 00:28:09,333
- [Voiceover] A fish in a boiling cauldron

349
00:28:09,333 --> 00:28:10,958
knows its days are numbered.

350
00:28:10,958 --> 00:28:12,375
Why would the bird who knows the nest

351
00:28:12,375 --> 00:28:14,083
is dangerous wait for the wind?

352
00:28:15,791 --> 00:28:18,166
- I never knew Conquerer's
Clan had such a poetic master.

353
00:28:18,166 --> 00:28:19,000
You are?

354
00:28:19,000 --> 00:28:21,291
- Names are useless, hence, I am Nameless.

355
00:28:22,333 --> 00:28:23,791
- Ao Jue, honored to meet you.

356
00:28:25,625 --> 00:28:26,541
- Ao Jue?

357
00:28:27,416 --> 00:28:29,458
So, you're from the Sword Worship Villa?

358
00:28:33,333 --> 00:28:36,291
Well, Jue, it seems you
haven't caught any fish today.

359
00:28:37,458 --> 00:28:40,750
- I've only caught small
ones but I want big game.

360
00:28:40,750 --> 00:28:43,500
- If you're looking for big
game, you should be weary,

361
00:28:43,500 --> 00:28:45,750
another bloody storm
could erupt at any moment.

362
00:28:46,916 --> 00:28:49,791
A storm such as this could be devastating.

363
00:28:49,791 --> 00:28:51,541
- Master Nameless, you worry too much.

364
00:28:51,541 --> 00:28:52,916
Look, the sky is clear.

365
00:28:54,666 --> 00:28:55,833
The big fish is here.

366
00:29:04,333 --> 00:29:05,458
- Once the big fish leaves,

367
00:29:05,458 --> 00:29:07,208
other fish can loose their bearings

368
00:29:07,208 --> 00:29:08,916
and things will turn to chaos.

369
00:29:11,083 --> 00:29:12,875
- The weak are nothing
but prey for the strong.

370
00:29:12,875 --> 00:29:14,291
This is simply nature.

371
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:18,000
And, definitely me.

372
00:29:20,333 --> 00:29:23,208
- Violence is in human nature
but it disrupts the peace.

373
00:29:25,583 --> 00:29:27,083
(exploding)

374
00:29:44,875 --> 00:29:45,666
(shouting)

375
00:29:52,958 --> 00:29:57,750
(somber music)

376
00:29:57,750 --> 00:29:59,833
Didn't Sword Worship
Villa make their weapons

377
00:29:59,833 --> 00:30:01,166
to uphold justice?

378
00:30:01,166 --> 00:30:04,250
- Justice, righteousness and
evil are all scholarly lies.

379
00:30:04,250 --> 00:30:06,958
Sword Worship Villa pledged
their loyalty to the Emperor,

380
00:30:06,958 --> 00:30:09,458
yet, why did he do what he
did and slaughter my family?

381
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:13,250
The Sword Worship Villa of old is gone.

382
00:30:13,250 --> 00:30:14,416
They were eliminated.

383
00:30:15,291 --> 00:30:18,125
My new clan is the Blade Manor.

384
00:30:18,125 --> 00:30:20,333
- Hate is the foundation of all evil.

385
00:30:20,333 --> 00:30:22,750
Young Master Jue, why
can't you leave behind

386
00:30:22,750 --> 00:30:25,458
that hate and live a life worth living?

387
00:30:25,458 --> 00:30:28,125
(clinking)

388
00:30:32,125 --> 00:30:35,375
- My nature is so merciless,
I have to be cold, too.

389
00:30:35,375 --> 00:30:37,208
Not everyone appreciates my music.

390
00:30:39,875 --> 00:30:44,875
(epic music)

391
00:32:01,583 --> 00:32:04,083
Ah, the Sword Shadow Technique.

392
00:32:13,750 --> 00:32:15,833
- [Nameless] This stubbornness
will do you no good.

393
00:32:15,833 --> 00:32:18,000
Let go of your anger.

394
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:21,083
(crashing)

395
00:32:25,833 --> 00:32:27,500
- No one in the world can stop me.

396
00:32:34,625 --> 00:32:37,208
- Hey, Ying, the Chao
Family's bodyguards are here.

397
00:32:42,333 --> 00:32:43,166
- I'll go deal with them.

398
00:32:43,166 --> 00:32:44,500
- Wait, Wood, stay calm.

399
00:32:47,291 --> 00:32:48,708
- You got nowhere to run now.

400
00:32:49,833 --> 00:32:50,791
Brat's pretty brave.

401
00:32:50,791 --> 00:32:52,666
How dare you steal Mr. Chao's dog.

402
00:32:54,250 --> 00:32:55,250
(thumping)

403
00:33:03,958 --> 00:33:07,041
(barking)

404
00:33:14,291 --> 00:33:15,708
- There's a martial arts master in there!

405
00:33:15,708 --> 00:33:16,625
Run!

406
00:33:21,583 --> 00:33:23,666
- Wow, Ying, he's good at martial arts.

407
00:33:26,125 --> 00:33:27,083
- So, what's your name?

408
00:33:31,875 --> 00:33:33,708
- I don't remember.

409
00:33:33,708 --> 00:33:35,291
- You don't remember your own name?

410
00:33:38,541 --> 00:33:40,250
- It doesn't matter if you don't know.

411
00:33:40,250 --> 00:33:41,625
You can work for me, now.

412
00:33:41,625 --> 00:33:42,458
- You're the youngest here.

413
00:33:42,458 --> 00:33:43,833
Why should he work for you?

414
00:33:46,166 --> 00:33:48,083
- What about now?

415
00:33:48,083 --> 00:33:49,916
- [Ying] Well, you're gonna need a name.

416
00:33:49,916 --> 00:33:51,625
Seeing as you're so good at martial arts,

417
00:33:51,625 --> 00:33:52,750
we'll call you Expert.

418
00:33:52,750 --> 00:33:54,083
You're one of us now, okay?

419
00:33:54,083 --> 00:33:55,708
- [Yang] Yeah, Expert's a great name.

420
00:33:56,916 --> 00:33:57,916
- [Voiceover] Mr. Chao is looking for

421
00:33:57,916 --> 00:33:59,666
some great bodyguards today.

422
00:33:59,666 --> 00:34:02,208
He'll choose the winner of
these martial arts contests.

423
00:34:06,708 --> 00:34:11,708
(fighting)

424
00:34:18,500 --> 00:34:19,791
We have a winner.

425
00:34:19,791 --> 00:34:22,083
It's Chen Dong of the Chen Fist Clan.

426
00:34:22,083 --> 00:34:23,125
Next fighter.

427
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:27,708
- Are they hiring bodyguards?

428
00:34:29,791 --> 00:34:30,583
- Is that wine?

429
00:34:30,583 --> 00:34:32,083
Is it the Drunken Fist?

430
00:34:32,083 --> 00:34:33,791
- But, we've already
chosen eight bodyguards,

431
00:34:33,791 --> 00:34:34,458
we don't need you.

432
00:34:34,458 --> 00:34:35,333
Move along.

433
00:34:37,208 --> 00:34:38,791
- Well, I'll take all eight of 'em on.

434
00:34:40,166 --> 00:34:41,041
- [Voiceover] How dare he?

435
00:34:41,041 --> 00:34:41,625
- [Voiceover] Rat.

436
00:34:45,000 --> 00:34:46,666
- Let's get him.

437
00:34:46,666 --> 00:34:51,333
(fighting)

438
00:34:51,333 --> 00:34:53,750
(exploding)

439
00:35:05,416 --> 00:35:06,583
(exploding)

440
00:35:12,625 --> 00:35:14,000
- Whoa, great!

441
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:15,083
He'll do for me.

442
00:35:15,083 --> 00:35:16,125
- The Wind Kick.

443
00:35:16,958 --> 00:35:18,041
- That means he's Wind.

444
00:35:18,041 --> 00:35:19,750
We should go tell the boss right away.

445
00:35:22,208 --> 00:35:23,500
- [Voiceover] Here's the money I owe you.

446
00:35:29,583 --> 00:35:31,500
- Mistress wants him
alive, what should we do?

447
00:35:31,500 --> 00:35:33,708
- Kill him first, we'll worry later.

448
00:35:33,708 --> 00:35:35,958
- But, the Mistress
won't look kindly on us.

449
00:35:35,958 --> 00:35:38,125
- Well, let's prepare some poison first.

450
00:35:38,125 --> 00:35:40,083
I'll convince Miss Dream it's for the best

451
00:35:40,083 --> 00:35:41,625
after we've killed him.

452
00:35:44,750 --> 00:35:46,458
(crickets chirping)

453
00:35:46,458 --> 00:35:51,416
(somber music)

454
00:36:14,291 --> 00:36:15,250
(glass breaking)

455
00:36:24,583 --> 00:36:29,458
(thrilling music)

456
00:36:32,750 --> 00:36:33,416
- Stop.

457
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:35,166
Look at that.

458
00:36:36,125 --> 00:36:38,125
It was he and Cloud who killed Conquerer.

459
00:36:40,916 --> 00:36:42,666
You almost killed a good man.

460
00:36:47,500 --> 00:36:50,416
(fire burning)

461
00:36:50,416 --> 00:36:53,541
(wind blowing)

462
00:36:55,833 --> 00:36:57,333
(horse whinnying)

463
00:37:03,291 --> 00:37:07,458
(crickets chirping)

464
00:37:07,458 --> 00:37:08,875
(horse whinnying)

465
00:37:09,958 --> 00:37:11,833
(owl hooting)

466
00:37:22,500 --> 00:37:24,000
- [Duen Long] Ghost Healer, stop now.

467
00:37:26,333 --> 00:37:27,333
(chuckling)

468
00:37:27,333 --> 00:37:28,208
- Long.

469
00:37:30,250 --> 00:37:32,791
(ominous music)

470
00:37:32,791 --> 00:37:33,916
- That smell.

471
00:37:33,916 --> 00:37:35,458
She smells so delicious.

472
00:37:35,458 --> 00:37:36,500
She's a woman?

473
00:37:36,500 --> 00:37:37,916
Well, what a waste.

474
00:37:41,125 --> 00:37:42,750
(horse whinnying)

475
00:37:42,750 --> 00:37:43,791
- So, where is it?

476
00:37:54,958 --> 00:37:56,375
(chuckling)

477
00:37:57,250 --> 00:38:00,333
- This toxic leech can
poison any human blood.

478
00:38:00,333 --> 00:38:01,708
This poison will work within a day

479
00:38:01,708 --> 00:38:03,625
of entering your victim's body.

480
00:38:03,625 --> 00:38:05,625
No matter how good his
martial arts powers,

481
00:38:05,625 --> 00:38:07,583
he'll still become fatally poisoned.

482
00:38:07,583 --> 00:38:09,875
He'll lose his strength
and won't be able to fight.

483
00:38:11,583 --> 00:38:13,583
- Ah, you're just as good as they say.

484
00:38:13,583 --> 00:38:15,333
If you need anything, let me know.

485
00:38:17,375 --> 00:38:18,916
- Another mild horse.

486
00:38:19,875 --> 00:38:20,666
- He's yours.

487
00:38:21,958 --> 00:38:24,375
I didn't tell you because
I didn't want to scare you.

488
00:38:24,375 --> 00:38:26,958
- But Long, can you really trust this guy?

489
00:38:26,958 --> 00:38:28,416
- [Duen Long] The Ghost
Healer's about as crazy

490
00:38:28,416 --> 00:38:30,250
as they come but as long as you give him

491
00:38:30,250 --> 00:38:33,208
what he wants, he'd even
betray his own parents.

492
00:38:33,208 --> 00:38:35,500
(growling)

493
00:38:35,500 --> 00:38:37,750
- You want to turn the Flame
Kylin's blood into poison

494
00:38:37,750 --> 00:38:40,041
with these leeches so
it'll destroy Jue after

495
00:38:40,041 --> 00:38:42,208
he extracts it from Wind
and Cloud and drinks it?

496
00:38:42,208 --> 00:38:45,500
- It's a necessary step to
kill two birds with one stone.

497
00:38:49,041 --> 00:38:50,208
- Hey, Expert, come here.

498
00:38:53,000 --> 00:38:54,375
What are you waiting for?

499
00:38:55,750 --> 00:38:57,416
You'll have to earn your keep here.

500
00:38:57,416 --> 00:38:58,750
So, let me show you how we do it.

501
00:38:58,750 --> 00:39:01,708
(funky music)

502
00:39:01,708 --> 00:39:03,125
- Excuse me, coming through.
- [Wood] There's so many

503
00:39:03,125 --> 00:39:04,666
people, hey, excuse me.

504
00:39:09,833 --> 00:39:10,750
(laughing)

505
00:39:10,750 --> 00:39:12,541
- Ow, that hurt, why you hitting me?

506
00:39:13,875 --> 00:39:14,958
- You're so useless.

507
00:39:15,958 --> 00:39:16,666
Watch me.

508
00:39:21,083 --> 00:39:22,291
- Let's see you do it.

509
00:39:33,875 --> 00:39:34,416
- I give up.

510
00:39:34,416 --> 00:39:36,625
How can you still see while
you're still blindfolded?

511
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:41,583
(laughing)

512
00:39:41,583 --> 00:39:43,041
- So, you think you're good, huh?

513
00:39:43,041 --> 00:39:44,416
Try and steal my money bag.

514
00:39:48,250 --> 00:39:49,875
Come on.

515
00:39:49,875 --> 00:39:52,208
(wind blowing)

516
00:39:53,125 --> 00:39:54,875
(jingling)

517
00:39:58,666 --> 00:39:59,625
You pervert.

518
00:40:07,750 --> 00:40:09,000
- [Juno] Don't do it.

519
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:10,208
- [Yam] Stop it, Expert.

520
00:40:17,083 --> 00:40:22,083
(calm music)

521
00:40:22,125 --> 00:40:24,541
(jingling)

522
00:40:28,208 --> 00:40:30,333
- Hey, Expert, as I saved your life,

523
00:40:30,333 --> 00:40:31,583
you owe me a big favor.

524
00:40:31,583 --> 00:40:33,583
- Sure, tell me what you want me to do.

525
00:40:40,541 --> 00:40:41,125
- We're here.

526
00:40:41,125 --> 00:40:42,583
Let's go get the doggie.

527
00:40:54,166 --> 00:40:55,750
Cool, that was so much fun.

528
00:40:58,500 --> 00:41:00,208
(clanking)

529
00:41:00,208 --> 00:41:01,333
- Shhh.

530
00:41:03,291 --> 00:41:08,000
