574
00:45:02,000 --> 00:45:03,833
- Oh, he's still breathing.

575
00:45:03,833 --> 00:45:06,250
- Why is everyone from
the South so darn strong?

576
00:45:10,583 --> 00:45:15,500
(ominous music)

577
00:45:40,875 --> 00:45:42,000
- [Young Jue] Father, why are we called

578
00:45:42,000 --> 00:45:43,750
the Sword Worship Villa?

579
00:45:43,750 --> 00:45:46,208
- A long time ago, our
great ancestors came

580
00:45:46,208 --> 00:45:48,291
across a piece of superior metal.

581
00:45:48,291 --> 00:45:49,625
