660
00:51:47,916 --> 00:51:48,750
I hope

661
00:51:50,958 --> 00:51:54,083
Wood, Bymie, Juno and Yam live good lives.

662
00:51:54,083 --> 00:51:57,791
I heard once, if you keep
heading towards the East,

663
00:51:57,791 --> 00:52:00,708
