664
00:52:00,708 --> 00:52:04,666
traveling East by boat, after
a month you'll find an island.

665
00:52:05,666 --> 00:52:07,583
The beautiful Peng Li Isle.

666
00:52:09,333 --> 00:52:10,916
When I've saved enough money,

667
00:52:10,916 --> 00:52:13,416
