01:03:17,666 --> 01:03:19,583
A man with a Kylin tattoo on his arm?

767
01:03:20,958 --> 01:03:23,583
(thunder booming)

768
01:03:23,583 --> 01:03:23,875
- Fish!

769
01:03:23,875 --> 01:03:24,666
- Yeah, it's a big one.

770
01:03:24,666 --> 01:03:25,708
We should catch it.

771
01:03:27,750 --> 01:03:28,958
Hey look, it's gone over there.

