You should just go, okay.

776
01:03:48,791 --> 01:03:50,125
You can be the captain of the guard

777
01:03:50,125 --> 01:03:52,041
and not have to hang out with us thieves.

778
01:03:56,208 --> 01:03:57,583
- I'm not going to be the captain.

779
01:04:03,833 --> 01:04:06,041
But, all of you should
stop stealing from people.

780
01:04:06,041 --> 01:04:07,333
Let me take care of you all.

781
01:04:09,666 --> 01:04:11,916
We'll find Peng Li Island together, okay.

782
01:04:17,708 --> 01:04:18,916
- That'll be great.

783
01:04:18,916 --> 01:04:21,208
