(suspenseful music)

801
01:05:43,083 --> 01:05:44,375
- Help me!

802
01:05:46,708 --> 01:05:48,208
(banging)

803
01:05:53,000 --> 01:05:55,500
(smashing)

804
01:05:56,625 --> 01:06:01,166
(heroic music)

805
01:06:03,500 --> 01:06:06,333
(crashing)

806
01:06:08,583 --> 01:06:09,500
- Hold on tight.

807
01:06:29,541 --> 01:06:31,500
(shouting)

808
01:06:33,291 --> 01:06:35,291
(cheering)

809
01:06:42,958 --> 01:06:46,250
(breaking)

810
01:06:47,125 --> 01:06:48,458
- [Yam] The baby birdies!

811
01:06:52,250 --> 01:06:55,750
(birds chirping)

812
01:07:03,916 --> 01:07:04,791
- [Ying] Are we all ready?

813
01:07:13,041 --> 01:07:13,750
- Get him.

814
01:07:18,833 --> 01:07:19,708
(laughing)

815
01:07:20,625 --> 01:07:22,500
- Wind, how did you and Cloud meet?

816
01:07:23,875 --> 01:07:26,166
- We both had an unhappy childhood.

817
01:07:26,166 --> 01:07:29,416
Our parents were killed by Conquerer.

818
01:07:29,416 --> 01:07:31,708
We both thought the same thing.

819
01:07:31,708 --> 01:07:34,333
For revenge, we first
had to look at our fight.

820
01:07:34,333 --> 01:07:35,791
- My name is Wind.

821
01:07:35,791 --> 01:07:39,666
(somber music)

822
01:07:39,666 --> 01:07:41,791
- Wind, Cloud.

823
01:07:43,083 --> 01:07:44,875
Fate has delivered you both to me.

824
01:07:46,000 --> 01:07:48,166
(laughing)

825
01:07:49,458 --> 01:07:51,791
- [Miss Dream] So, what
was he like before?

826
01:07:51,791 --> 01:07:54,125
- [Wind] Our personalities
were totally different.

827
01:07:57,000 --> 01:07:59,625
(growling)

828
01:07:59,625 --> 01:08:00,875
(shouting)

829
01:08:17,041 --> 01:08:19,208
(whimpering)

830
01:08:26,625 --> 01:08:27,625
(gasping)

831
01:08:28,875 --> 01:08:31,000
- Why did you have to kill them?

832
01:08:31,000 --> 01:08:32,750
- They can't protect themselves like this.

833
01:08:32,750 --> 01:08:34,208
It's a blessing for them to die young

834
01:08:34,208 --> 01:08:36,125
rather than suffer a life of pain.

835
01:08:40,708 --> 01:08:42,750
- The Cloud I've known for all these years

836
01:08:42,750 --> 01:08:44,541
is not the same man now.

837
01:08:44,541 --> 01:08:47,083
- [Miss Dream] Are you going
to tell him about his past?

838
01:08:47,083 --> 01:08:49,500
- No, I've never seen him
smile like this before.

839
01:08:51,083 --> 01:08:52,500
- It's a blessing for him.

840
01:08:52,500 --> 01:08:53,375
He seems happy.

841
01:08:54,791 --> 01:08:57,333
I hope my father can be
happy where he is, too.

842
01:08:58,416 --> 01:08:59,666
- Your father?

843
01:08:59,666 --> 01:09:01,375
- My father left our family to become

844
01:09:01,375 --> 01:09:03,416
the best martial arts expert.

845
01:09:03,416 --> 01:09:05,000
Even when my mother passed away,

846
01:09:05,000 --> 01:09:06,041
he didn't come back.

847
01:09:06,041 --> 01:09:07,291
I hated him for it.

848
01:09:08,958 --> 01:09:10,291
But, when my mother died,

849
01:09:10,291 --> 01:09:12,750
she said she felt no hate or regret.

850
01:09:12,750 --> 01:09:15,500
It changed the way I thought.

851
01:09:15,500 --> 01:09:17,750
In my heart, I know my mother was hoping

852
01:09:17,750 --> 01:09:19,666
I would give my father another chance

853
01:09:19,666 --> 01:09:20,791
and forgive him.

854
01:09:22,625 --> 01:09:27,291
(somber music)

855
01:09:29,125 --> 01:09:30,750
(laughing)

856
01:09:33,458 --> 01:09:35,000
- Revenge is a vicious cycle.

857
01:09:36,416 --> 01:09:38,833
Cloud and I spent half our
lives planning revenge.

858
01:09:39,958 --> 01:09:42,041
But, neither of us knew

859
01:09:42,041 --> 01:09:43,875
revenge doesn't bring peace or joy.

860
01:09:44,916 --> 01:09:47,166
Cloud was known as the God of Death.

861
01:09:47,166 --> 01:09:49,291
I never could've imagined this.

862
01:09:49,291 --> 01:09:50,666
The moment his past is forgotten

863
01:09:50,666 --> 01:09:52,750
marks the beginning of his happiness.

864
01:09:52,750 --> 01:09:54,666
It seems if you leave the anger behind,

865
01:09:54,666 --> 01:09:56,083
a new life begins.

866
01:09:57,791 --> 01:09:59,750
(yelling)

867
01:09:59,750 --> 01:10:02,083
- [Yam] Hey, Mr. Wind, come play with us.

868
01:10:11,625 --> 01:10:16,333
(peaceful music)

869
01:10:24,583 --> 01:10:25,666
- You know, this is the first time

870
01:10:25,666 --> 01:10:27,625
I've seen you happy since I met you.

871
01:10:27,625 --> 01:10:29,416
- We've never really
played like this before.

872
01:10:29,416 --> 01:10:31,500
So, I feel quite happy.

873
01:10:31,500 --> 01:10:32,833
- I'm happy for you, too.

874
01:10:32,833 --> 01:10:35,333
You've finally found your good brother.

875
01:10:35,333 --> 01:10:37,291
- And, someone else who cares for me.

876
01:10:38,708 --> 01:10:43,083
(romantic music)

877
01:11:08,708 --> 01:11:09,500
Dream.

878
01:11:10,833 --> 01:11:14,125
I'll stay with you and wait
for your father's return.

879
01:11:42,708 --> 01:11:47,458
(banging)

880
01:11:48,833 --> 01:11:51,916
- Life is always full of
ups and downs, Master Wind.

881
01:11:51,916 --> 01:11:54,791
At this moment, do you feel as
though life has blessed you?

882
01:11:57,541 --> 01:12:00,250
If you wish for your brother
to feel the same happiness,

883
01:12:00,250 --> 01:12:02,291
you should leave this place immediately.

884
01:12:03,375 --> 01:12:05,666
In your blood runs the spirit of the Kylin

885
01:12:05,666 --> 01:12:08,416
and the Kylin's nemesis
is none other than Cloud.

886
01:12:10,416 --> 01:12:12,208
Wind and Cloud will make you.

887
01:12:13,250 --> 01:12:15,875
Yet, Wind and Cloud will break you.

888
01:12:15,875 --> 01:12:19,791
See, the lives of Wind
and Cloud are intertwined

889
01:12:19,791 --> 01:12:22,125
in life but also with death.

890
01:12:22,125 --> 01:12:24,000
If you both want good lives,

891
01:12:24,000 --> 01:12:26,000
you'll have to live apart from each other

892
01:12:26,000 --> 01:12:28,833
and stay away from the martial arts world.

893
01:12:28,833 --> 01:12:33,500
(pleasant music)

894
01:12:40,291 --> 01:12:41,625
- He died because of you?

895
01:12:41,625 --> 01:12:43,833
If you're brother knew you
lived with such regret,

896
01:12:43,833 --> 01:12:45,958
I'm sure he would forgive you.

897
01:12:45,958 --> 01:12:47,166
- I know he'd forgive me.

898
01:12:47,166 --> 01:12:48,791
I just hope he's found a better place

899
01:12:48,791 --> 01:12:51,291
and can live in happier times.

900
01:12:51,291 --> 01:12:54,541
Will you please have a drink
with me and my brother?

901
01:12:54,541 --> 01:12:55,250
- Sure.

902
01:13:07,208 --> 01:13:08,875
- I'll be leaving soon.

903
01:13:08,875 --> 01:13:09,666
- Why's that?

904
01:13:11,625 --> 01:13:13,375
- I have to find my place in the world.

905
01:13:18,750 --> 01:13:20,291
The promise my brother made me,

906
01:13:20,291 --> 01:13:21,958
if it were you, would you have killed me?

907
01:13:23,041 --> 01:13:26,375
- Yes, because we're
brothers and you asked me to.

908
01:13:29,708 --> 01:13:30,541
Take care.

909
01:13:40,708 --> 01:13:44,875
(ominous music)

910
01:13:46,500 --> 01:13:47,166
- Dream.

911
01:14:17,208 --> 01:14:18,791
- It's Kay.

912
01:14:18,791 --> 01:14:19,666
- Deal with her.

913
01:14:29,375 --> 01:14:33,083
(yelling)

914
01:14:37,750 --> 01:14:40,916
(growling)

915
01:14:51,208 --> 01:14:52,416
- Wind, are you okay?

916
01:14:56,166 --> 01:14:58,750
- Striding Cloud!

917
01:15:08,416 --> 01:15:09,250
(breaking)

918
01:15:13,000 --> 01:15:13,833
- Wind!

919
01:15:22,458 --> 01:15:23,750
Wind, please stop!

920
01:15:29,916 --> 01:15:31,166
It's me, Wind.

921
01:15:44,208 --> 01:15:45,291
- [Shadow] Stop there.

922
01:15:51,291 --> 01:15:52,416
- We can't let her get away.

923
01:15:52,416 --> 01:15:54,250
- You two really think you can stop me?

924
01:15:57,833 --> 01:16:01,750
(foreboding music)

925
01:16:01,750 --> 01:16:03,791
(breaking)

926
01:16:09,458 --> 01:16:11,666
- [Quail] Quickly, get Captain Xi.

927
01:16:11,666 --> 01:16:13,125
- I'm only here for Wind and Cloud.

928
01:16:13,125 --> 01:16:14,500
Get out of the way or die.

929
01:16:21,500 --> 01:16:25,833
(gasping)

930
01:16:25,833 --> 01:16:26,791
- You.

931
01:16:28,083 --> 01:16:29,041
- Shadow.

932
01:16:44,250 --> 01:16:49,000
(fighting)

933
01:16:49,916 --> 01:16:51,250
- You wanna die?

934
01:17:00,041 --> 01:17:01,000
- I'm the captain of the guard.

935
01:17:01,000 --> 01:17:02,375
I have to protect this city.

936
01:17:05,333 --> 01:17:10,333
(ominous music)

937
01:17:14,291 --> 01:17:16,666
Oh, Quail, you fool.

938
01:17:16,666 --> 01:17:18,875
Why on earth didn't you wait for me.

939
01:17:21,916 --> 01:17:23,333
I'm the captain of the guard.

940
01:17:23,333 --> 01:17:25,208
You wanna fight, then fight me.

941
01:17:36,083 --> 01:17:40,000
(gasping)

942
01:17:40,000 --> 01:17:43,125
(rattling)

943
01:17:57,208 --> 01:17:59,333
- The blood of the Flame
Kylin's almost mine.

944
01:18:01,500 --> 01:18:03,125
- Please, Master Jue, help me.

945
01:18:10,958 --> 01:18:12,000
- Look, it's Wind.

946
01:18:14,958 --> 01:18:16,166
- Take him alive.

947
01:18:18,166 --> 01:18:23,041
(epic music)

948
01:18:26,583 --> 01:18:31,583
(fighting)

949
01:19:18,875 --> 01:19:19,791
- How do you like this?

950
01:19:19,791 --> 01:19:22,041
I designed this Kylin
lock especially for you.

951
01:19:26,166 --> 01:19:27,333
- [Juno] We have to help Wind.

952
01:19:27,333 --> 01:19:28,291
- [Wood] Yeah, shoot him.

953
01:19:33,625 --> 01:19:36,583
(breaking)

954
01:19:43,916 --> 01:19:44,791
Yam, watch out!

955
01:19:44,791 --> 01:19:47,375
(yelling)

956
01:19:56,791 --> 01:20:01,791
(somber music)

957
01:20:05,916 --> 01:20:08,000
- It really doesn't matter
if I'm this Striding Cloud

958
01:20:08,000 --> 01:20:08,625
or not.

959
01:20:08,625 --> 01:20:10,791
What's most important right now

960
01:20:10,791 --> 01:20:11,958
is that we're friends.

961
01:20:12,875 --> 01:20:15,041
After I save Wind, I'll come back

962
01:20:15,041 --> 01:20:16,833
and we'll go to Peng Li Isle, okay.

963
01:20:19,791 --> 01:20:24,458
(horse galloping)

964
01:20:30,083 --> 01:20:34,791
(ominous music)

965
01:20:52,958 --> 01:20:56,125
- Master Jue, I'm sorry, I was too slow

966
01:20:56,125 --> 01:20:58,875
and I couldn't stop Wind from killing Kay.

967
01:20:58,875 --> 01:21:01,000
But, as soon as you drink
the Flame Kylin's blood,

968
01:21:01,000 --> 01:21:02,541
not even Nameless can stop you.

969
01:21:02,541 --> 01:21:04,208
Soon, the whole martial arts world

970
01:21:04,208 --> 01:21:05,416
will bow before you.

971
01:21:11,666 --> 01:21:12,708
A blood leech.

972
01:21:14,125 --> 01:21:16,708
- Kay's would was inflicted
by the Kylin Sword.

973
01:21:16,708 --> 01:21:19,791
You think a master swordsmith
is so easily fooled?

974
01:21:19,791 --> 01:21:22,500
Are you thinking about
the Ghost Healer now?

975
01:21:22,500 --> 01:21:23,958
I invited him earlier.

976
01:21:28,083 --> 01:21:30,208
(laughing)

977
01:21:41,625 --> 01:21:42,958
Did you think I wanted to drink the blood

978
01:21:42,958 --> 01:21:44,708
of the Flame Kylin?

979
01:21:44,708 --> 01:21:46,208
I wanted the blood for one thing.

980
01:21:46,208 --> 01:21:48,083
To break the seal binding this sword.

981
01:21:48,958 --> 01:21:50,833
I don't just want the martial arts world,

982
01:21:51,708 --> 01:21:53,791
I want everything under the sky.

983
01:21:53,791 --> 01:21:58,625
(foreboding music)

984
01:22:00,416 --> 01:22:02,916
(shouting)

985
01:22:07,583 --> 01:22:12,583
(epic music)

986
01:22:20,583 --> 01:22:21,375
- Take him alive!

987
01:22:39,833 --> 01:22:44,708
(fighting)

988
01:23:01,083 --> 01:23:02,000
You wanna save him?

989
01:23:02,000 --> 01:23:03,958
I'll trade him for the
Kylin blood in your body.

990
01:23:18,458 --> 01:23:19,250
- Wind.

991
01:23:29,208 --> 01:23:30,125
- Let him go.

992
01:23:40,416 --> 01:23:42,541
- With the Ao ancestors as
witness, I shall release

993
01:23:42,541 --> 01:23:45,416
the Jue Sword from the
Flame Kylin's blood.

994
01:23:45,416 --> 01:23:47,416
I'm not afraid of a
curse on my descendants.

995
01:23:47,416 --> 01:23:49,666
To achieve my revenge, I have no regrets.

996
01:23:57,625 --> 01:23:59,916
(laughing)

997
01:24:20,833 --> 01:24:22,583
Man and sword unite.

998
01:24:22,583 --> 01:24:23,791
- Release my friend now.

999
01:24:29,000 --> 01:24:30,833
- Yes, a great blade

1000
01:24:30,833 --> 01:24:32,250
and it will taste your blood.

1001
01:24:38,500 --> 01:24:43,375
(epic music)

1002
01:24:54,333 --> 01:24:59,333
(fighting)

1003
01:25:28,916 --> 01:25:32,208
This sword is truly
the king of all swords.

1004
01:25:51,875 --> 01:25:56,583
(fighting)

1005
01:26:26,041 --> 01:26:27,375
Nameless.

1006
01:26:27,375 --> 01:26:28,666
- Ao Jue.

1007
01:26:28,666 --> 01:26:30,000
Turn back from evil.

1008
01:26:43,458 --> 01:26:48,416
(ominous music)

1009
01:27:41,166 --> 01:27:45,666
(epic music)

1010
01:27:53,000 --> 01:27:54,375
That sword is beyond evil.

1011
01:27:54,375 --> 01:27:56,250
It would even kill its own master.

1012
01:27:56,250 --> 01:27:57,500
Give it up.

1013
01:27:57,500 --> 01:27:58,416
- Shut up.

1014
01:27:58,416 --> 01:28:01,416
After I kill you I'll be the
greatest fighter in the world.

1015
01:28:01,416 --> 01:28:06,000
(fighting)

1016
01:28:06,000 --> 01:28:07,250
No one.

1017
01:28:07,250 --> 01:28:08,416
No one can kill me.

1018
01:28:11,416 --> 01:28:15,041
(shouting)

1019
01:28:15,041 --> 01:28:16,541
- The Devil Shadow Technique.

1020
01:28:40,583 --> 01:28:43,791
- Ao Jue's makes you a saint
but evil only begets evil.

1021
01:28:43,791 --> 01:28:45,375
My Sword of the Heavens will break

1022
01:28:45,375 --> 01:28:46,750
the Sword of the Devil.

1023
01:29:05,625 --> 01:29:10,333
(awe-inspiring music)

1024
01:29:27,000 --> 01:29:27,458
Be careful.

1025
01:29:27,458 --> 01:29:28,416
Drop the sword.

1026
01:29:34,250 --> 01:29:37,208
(screaming)

1027
01:29:38,291 --> 01:29:39,916
(screaming)

1028
01:29:43,000 --> 01:29:45,250
If the Jue Sword's demon
soul gets into your body,

1029
01:29:45,250 --> 01:29:46,708
you'll become the Kylin Devil.

1030
01:29:54,208 --> 01:29:58,208
(shouting)

1031
01:30:13,750 --> 01:30:15,041
- The devils of the storms.

1032
01:30:15,041 --> 01:30:17,041
Wind and Cloud will fight to the death.

1033
01:30:17,041 --> 01:30:19,458
They won't stop until
one or both are slain.

1034
01:30:19,458 --> 01:30:20,708
If you wish to save them,

1035
01:30:20,708 --> 01:30:22,416
then I suggest you release me.

1036
01:30:31,500 --> 01:30:36,375
(fighting)

1037
01:30:48,083 --> 01:30:49,333
- Tell me how we can save them.

1038
01:30:49,333 --> 01:30:50,500
- Use that sword.

1039
01:30:50,500 --> 01:30:52,666
Use the Kylin Sword to
draw out the Kylin Blood

1040
01:30:52,666 --> 01:30:53,750
in their bodies.

1041
01:30:53,750 --> 01:30:55,458
Only then can they return to normal.

1042
01:30:56,541 --> 01:31:01,333
(fighting)

1043
01:31:21,041 --> 01:31:25,916
(epic music)

1044
01:32:40,458 --> 01:32:44,625
(crumbling)

1045
01:32:44,625 --> 01:32:47,125
(shouting)

1046
01:33:33,333 --> 01:33:35,291
- Ying, Wind's over here.

1047
01:33:36,333 --> 01:33:37,000
Come help me.

1048
01:33:41,291 --> 01:33:43,208
- [Ying] If you wanna kill
her, you have to go through me.

1049
01:33:53,333 --> 01:33:57,458
(shouting)

1050
01:33:59,958 --> 01:34:03,125
(yelling)

1051
01:34:05,750 --> 01:34:06,708
- Oh no, Ying!

1052
01:34:19,833 --> 01:34:21,291
- I'm just glad you're fine.

1053
01:34:26,916 --> 01:34:28,333
- You have to kill Wind now.

1054
01:34:28,333 --> 01:34:30,083
He's lost all his humanity.

1055
01:34:30,083 --> 01:34:32,000
There's no turning back for him.

1056
01:34:32,000 --> 01:34:32,750
- No.

1057
01:34:36,416 --> 01:34:37,666
I'll save him, I will.

1058
01:34:38,875 --> 01:34:40,625
There has to be a way to save him.

1059
01:34:55,208 --> 01:34:56,875
This won't end unless you kill him.

1060
01:35:06,208 --> 01:35:11,041
(birds squawking)

1061
01:35:17,958 --> 01:35:20,958
- But, Cloud, don't you wanna
find out about your past?

1062
01:35:21,791 --> 01:35:24,958
- That day, when Wind
asked me if I were Cloud

1063
01:35:24,958 --> 01:35:26,416
would I have been able to kill him,

1064
01:35:27,500 --> 01:35:29,375
the old me would've said yes.

1065
01:35:29,375 --> 01:35:30,791
But, I've changed.

1066
01:35:30,791 --> 01:35:32,583
Now, I'll never give up on a friend.

1067
01:35:33,708 --> 01:35:36,375
From now on, I'll only
remember happier days.

1068
01:35:37,458 --> 01:35:42,250
- Huh, Cloud, Ying, I can see the island!

1069
01:35:42,250 --> 01:35:46,583
(happy music)

